@startuml
!theme plain
title Data Flow for COVID-19 Data Engineering Project

participant "AWS Open Data Registry" as Registry
participant "S3 Data Lake" as S3
participant "AWS Athena" as Athena
participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
participant "Pandas DataFrame" as Pandas
participant "Amazon Redshift" as Redshift

Registry -> S3: Store raw COVID-19 datasets
S3 -> Athena: Query raw data
Athena -> Notebook: Extract data into DataFrames
Notebook -> Pandas: Transform and model data
Pandas -> Notebook: Return processed DataFrames
Notebook -> S3: Save transformed data as CSV
Notebook -> Redshift: Create tables (SQL statements)
Notebook -> Redshift: Load dimensional model data
@enduml